    }

    /**
     Creates a new {@link Connection} to use as a session. Connection settings (user-agent, timeouts, URL, etc), and
     cookies will be maintained for the session. Use examples:
<pre><code>
Connection session = Jsoup.newSession()
     .timeout(20 * 1000)
